txt.en: 'Have you defeated whatever vile thing is leading the invaders within Stangraf?'
Eliminate the leader of the forces of Isengard within Stangraf.
'Ah, the little one has returned victorious! No more ore for Saruman's cause.'
You should return to Quickbeam and inform him of your success within Stangraf.\n\nQuickbeam can be found at Derndingle.
As you approach the Horse, you hear Elfward shout across the yard to you.\n\n'Trust in this Horse to lead you to Stangraf. He is sure-footed and knows the way well!'
Defeated the leader of the invaders in Stangraf
Stangraf is no longer empty, and Quickbeam has sent you to the mine with the task of defeating the leader of whatever resides in the miners' worksite.
Defeat the leader of the invaders in Stangraf

'Isengard wanes, but there are still small pockets Saruman can use to rebuild. One is Stangraf, a mine. I cannot enter there myself, but you are small. Defeat the new occupants within the mine.\n\n'When you are ready, I will show you where these caves can be found.'
You gather your belongings and prepare for the journey to Stangraf.
